reviewText: I am following the career of Daniel Henney and viewing his work to see if and how he has grown as an actor. The movie was above average, enjoyable, and easy to watch.
Funny and is Daniel Henney smexy!!!

This movie is absolutely amazing!! I am an action lover and this movie did not disappoint! Aaaand..the comedy...had me in stitches. Let's not forget... Daniel Henney was just awesome! He is definitely a guy that makes being bad look OH SO good! I just love this movie! I am so glad I bought it! I've watched it 5 times since.
